---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Terms & Conditions - OPTYP" 
  description="Terms and Conditions for OPTYP professional resume and profile optimization services.">

  <section class="relative py-20 px-6 bg-gradient-to-br from-black via-gray-900 to-black text-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-4xl font-body">

      <!-- Header -->
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-4 text-white">Terms & Conditions</h1>
        <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-400 to-green-500 mx-auto mb-8 rounded-full shadow-sm"></div>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
          By using OPTYP services, you agree to comply with the following terms and conditions. 
          Please read these terms carefully before engaging our services.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-400">
          Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Content -->
      <article class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none space-y-12 text-gray-300">

        <!-- Service Agreement -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-teal-400 font-bold text-2xl mb-4">1. Service Agreement</h2>
          <div class="glass-box p-6 rounded-xl">
            <p>
              By engaging OPTYP's services, you enter a binding agreement to receive professional resume 
              and profile optimization as described in your plan.
            </p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mt-4 space-y-2">
              <li>Services include ATS-compliant resumes, LinkedIn optimization, portfolio website development</li>
              <li>Service delivery timelines are specified in your package details</li>
              <li>All services are delivered digitally unless stated otherwise</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Client Responsibilities -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-teal-400 font-bold text-2xl mb-4">2. Client Responsibilities</h2>
          <p class="font-semibold mb-4">To ensure effective service, you agree to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Provide accurate, truthful, and up-to-date career information</li>
            <li>Respond promptly to information requests</li>
            <li>Collaborate closely with our team</li>
            <li>Review and approve deliverables within review periods</li>
            <li>Use our services lawfully and ethically</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- Payment Terms -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-teal-400 font-bold text-2xl mb-4">3. Payment Terms</h2>
          <div class="glass-box p-6 rounded-xl border border-green-500/40">
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>Full payment required prior to service commencement</li>
              <li>Prices listed in Indian Rupees (â‚¹), subject to change</li>
              <li>Accepted payment methods include credit/debit cards and digital wallets</li>
              <li>Payments are non-refundable unless covered by our refund policy</li>
              <li>Suspension of service for delayed or non-payment</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Intellectual Property -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-teal-400 font-bold text-2xl mb-4">4. Intellectual Property Rights</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="glass-box p-4 rounded-lg border border-yellow-500/40">
              <p class="font-semibold text-yellow-300">Your Content Ownership</p>
              <p>All delivered content becomes your property upon full payment.</p>
            </div>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>You retain ownership over your personal data and career content</li>
              <li>OPTYP retains intellectual property rights on methodologies and templates</li>
              <li>Deliverables are for your personal professional use only</li>
              <li>Resale or redistribution of proprietary methodologies is prohibited</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Service Guarantees -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-teal-400 font-bold text-2xl mb-4">5. Service Guarantees & Limitations</h2>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div class="glass-box p-6 rounded-xl border border-green-500/40">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-green-300 mb-3">What We Guarantee</h3>
              <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 text-sm">
                <li>ATS-compliant resume formatting</li>
                <li>Professional optimization of content</li>
                <li>Timely delivery as per agreements</li>
                <li>Two rounds of revisions included</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="glass-box p-6 rounded-xl border border-red-500/40">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-red-300 mb-3">What We Cannot Guarantee</h3>
              <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1 text-sm">
                <li>Job interview or employment outcomes</li>
                <li>Response rates from employers</li>
                <li>Results from factors outside our control</li>
                <li>Compatibility with all ATS systems</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Limitation of Liability -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-teal-400 font-bold text-2xl mb-4">6. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <div class="glass-box p-6 rounded-xl">
            <p>Liability for services is limited to amounts paid. We disclaim liability for:</p>
            <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
              <li>Indirect or consequential damages</li>
              <li>Lost profits or business opportunities</li>
              <li>Third-party actions</li>
              <li>Technical issues beyond control</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Confidentiality -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-teal-400 font-bold text-2xl mb-4">7. Confidentiality</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Usage limited to service provision</li>
            <li>No sharing without consent</li>
            <li>Confidentiality agreements for all staff</li>
            <li>Secure data handling policies</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- Termination -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-teal-400 font-bold text-2xl mb-4">8. Termination</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
            <li>Completion of contracted services</li>
            <li>Mutual consent</li>
            <li>Material breach of terms</li>
            <li>Non-payment or non-cooperation</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <!-- Governing Law -->
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-teal-400 font-bold text-2xl mb-4">9. Governing Law</h2>
          <p>These terms are governed by the laws of India. Disputes shall be resolved through binding arbitration under Indian law.</p>
        </section>

        <!-- Contact -->
        <section class="bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-500 to-green-500 text-white p-8 rounded-xl text-center shadow-xl">
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Questions About Our Terms?</h2>
          <p class="mb-6">For any inquiries regarding these Terms and Conditions, please reach out to our support team.</p>
          <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:info@optyp.com" class="underline hover:text-gray-200">info@optyp.com</a></p>
          <p><strong>Contact Form:</strong> <a href="/contact/" class="underline hover:text-gray-200">Visit our Contact Page</a></p>
        </section>

      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .glass-box {
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
      border: 1px solid rgba(20,184,166,0.4); /* teal accent border */
      border-radius: 1rem;
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.6);
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
